These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, skiing
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | fanta | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Sport      | skateboarding    | weightlifting  | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, coffee
There are 3 different nationalities: german, russian, indian
1. the german is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the russian is on the far left##1
3. the russian is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | coffee      |
| Nationality   | russian | german | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, fanta
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, potato, cherry
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta  | juice       |
| Food       | lettuce     | potato | cherry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, peach, grapefruit
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, rock-climbing, sudoku
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | grapefruit    | peach     | apricot |
| Hobby   | sudoku | reading | rock-climbing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, frog
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, tram
1. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the frog##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | snake | lizard     | frog |
| Transport   | tram        | boat | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, tomato, grapefruit
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, taxi
1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | grapefruit | asparagus      | tomato  |
| Transport   | helicopter       | roller | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, trance, punk
3 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, cat
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of trance is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | pop     | trance    |
| Pet           | hamster | cat | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
