The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, rock-climbing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person eating spinach is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | watermelon | lemon | spinach      |
| Hobby   | singing     | video-games | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, fishing
3 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, mouse
1. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | fishing | traveling | magic-tricks  |
| Pet     | mouse     | ferret      | dog |

