.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, lemonade
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, martial-arts
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | 7up    | lemonade    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | scientific | martial-arts |

