.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, house
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, australian, russian
1. the fan of house is the nigerian##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the russian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | house   | dubstep  |
| Nationality   | russian    | nigerian | australian |

