.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, lime, pear
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, project-manager, chef
1. the project-manager is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the person eating pear is in the middle##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | blueberry     | pear   | lime     |
| Job    | chef | project-manager | musician |

