.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, jazz, metal
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | lemonade | fanta  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | metal   | trance |

