There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, french, spanish
1. the spanish is on the far left##1
2. the police-officer is on the far right##1
3. the chinese is the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | designer | architect | police-officer |
| Nationality   | spanish  | chinese      | french |

