The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person eating apple is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | lettuce | lemon   | apple        |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | golf | rowing |

