1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | traveling | filmmaking | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | classical | punk     | reggae  |

