.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, pineapple, cabbage
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, golf, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is golf is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | cabbage | strawberry       | pineapple  |
| Sport   | volleyball  | golf | badminton |

 